Haví<0xC5><0x99>ov's "deregulation" desk is certainly not overwhelmed with questions.
"Out of yesterday's 360 clients, there were only about forty to fifty people here for rent for 2011," the workers behind the counter estimate.
RPG suggests individual contract negotiation on the web and on its boards where it is needed.
However, if both parties do not agree on the lease, it will have to be determined by an independent court.
