The salmon steak for dinner was the "richest" with 34 chemical residues discovered, and even an analysis of the plastic plate used to heat food in the microwave oven did not escape the analysis.
The ultimate risk to consumers of this "cocktail of contaminants" is likely to be underestimated, according to the study.
The Ecological Europe-Greens Association (EE-LV) has proposed "in the face of an emergency" to establish a moratorium on the use of pesticides to stop the "growth of civilizational diseases".
